      "title": "MBSL Insurance expands its reach",
      "author": "Sahan Weerasooriya",
      "body_lines": [
        "MBSL Insurance Company Limited opened its newest fully-fledged branch in the city of Ambalantota recently to cater to the insurance needs of the local community. The company aims to expand and strengthen its reach throughout the nation to serve its customers better. The new branch is located at No. 133/1 (First Floor), Main Street, Ambalantota.",
        "MBSL Insurance offers a wider range of General Insurance products to meet every customer need, including both motor and non-motor insurance. The company strives to provide the highest service standards with a total spectrum of protection.",
        "MBSL Insurance Chairman D. P. K. Gunasekera (Former General Manager of Bank of Ceylon), CEO Rukman Weeraratne, Members of the Management, Buddhika Premaratna (AGM, Bank of Ceylon \u2013 Southern) and Distinguished Guests from Bank of Ceylon, MBSL and other organizations attended the opening ceremony.",
        "Profit-takings in blue chip counters put an end to bourse\u2019s bullish run",
        "Hela Apparel Holdings marks an impressive start to FY 2022/23",
